{"id":536,"parent_id":497,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":536,"title":"Psalm 39","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ps.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Psalm 39"],[".studySummary",["i","David seeks to control his tongue—Man is altogether vanity—He is a stranger and a sojourner on the earth."]],[".intro","To the chief Musician,",["i","even"],"to Jeduthun, A Psalm of David."]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.1","order":"02.20.039.36537"},["b","1"],"I said, I will take heed to my ways, that I sin not with my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"tongue"],": I will keep my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"mouth"],"with a bridle, while the wicked is before me."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.2","order":"02.20.039.36538"},["b","2"],"I was dumb with silence, I held my peace,",["i","even"],"from good; and my sorrow was stirred."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.3","order":"02.20.039.36539"},["b","3"],"My heart was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"hot"],"within me, while I was musing the fire burned:",["i","then"],"spake I with my tongue,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.4","order":"02.20.039.36540"},["b","4"],["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", make me to know mine end, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"measure"],"of my days, what it",["i","is; that"],"I may know how frail I",["i","am."]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.5","order":"02.20.039.36541"},["b","5"],"Behold, thou hast made my days",["i","as"],"an handbreadth; and mine age",["i","is"],"as nothing before thee: verily every man at his best state",["i","is"],"altogether",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"vanity"],".",["i","Selah"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.6","order":"02.20.039.36542"},["b","6"],"Surely every man walketh in a vain shew: surely they are disquieted in vain: he heapeth up",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"riches"],","],"and knoweth not who shall gather them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.7","order":"02.20.039.36543"},["b","7"],"And now, Lord, what wait I for? my hope",["i","is"],"in thee."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.8","order":"02.20.039.36544"},["b","8"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Deliver"],"me from all my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"transgressions"],": make me not the reproach of the foolish."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.9","order":"02.20.039.36545"},["b","9"],"I was dumb, I opened not my mouth; because thou didst",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.10","order":"02.20.039.36546"},["b","10"],"Remove thy stroke away from me: I am consumed by the blow of thine hand."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.11","order":"02.20.039.36547"},["b","11"],"When thou with rebukes dost",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"correct"],"man for iniquity, thou makest his beauty to consume away like a moth: surely every man",["i","is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"vanity"],".",["i","Selah"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.12","order":"02.20.039.36548"},["b","12"],"Hear my prayer, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and give ear unto my cry; hold not thy peace at my tears: for I",["i","am"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"stranger"],"with thee,",["i","and"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"sojourner"],", as all my fathers",["i","were."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.13","order":"02.20.039.36549"},["b","13"],"O spare me, that I may recover strength, before I go hence, and be no more."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.1a","order":"02.20.039.36550"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.2.1-13"},"James 3:2 (1–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.1b","order":"02.20.039.36552"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/141.3"},"Ps. 141:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.3a","order":"02.20.039.36554"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.9"},"Jer. 20:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.4a","order":"02.20.039.36556"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.84"},"Ps. 119:84"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.5a","order":"02.20.039.36558"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/40.15"},"Isa. 40:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/4.35"},"Dan. 4:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.6a","order":"02.20.039.36560"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.8a","order":"02.20.039.36562"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.8b","order":"02.20.039.36564"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"TG Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.11a","order":"02.20.039.36566"},["b","11a"],["span.small","OR"],"chasten."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.11b","order":"02.20.039.36568"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vanity"},"TG Vanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.12a","order":"02.20.039.36570"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/39.12b","order":"02.20.039.36572"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.3"},"Gen. 26:3"],"."]]}
